  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to try to evaluate the maturation of the autonomic nervous
      system in prematures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the maturation of the autonomic nervous system in prematures by using heart rate
      variability analyses.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
